OL,3,CJohn Lewis confirms plans to cut
OL,4,Cworkforce over the next five years
OL,6,Fhas confirmed to ITV News that it will
OL,7,Fbe looking to reduce the size of its
OL,8,Fworkforce as part of a wider plan to
OL,9,F"return to profit" over the next five
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FIt follows a Guardian report,
OL,13,Fpublished on Saturday, that said the
OL,14,FJohn Lewis Partnership (JLP) was
OL,15,Flooking to slash up to 11,000 jobs -
OL,16,F10% of its workforce - across the
OL,17,Fgroup's head office, supermarkets and
OL,18,Fdepartment stores.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/9
