OL,3,CJohn Lewis confirms plans to cut
OL,4,Cworkforce over the next five years
OL,6,FThe statement to ITV News did not
OL,7,Fconfirm the number of jobs that would
OL,8,Fbe cut.
OL,10,FIt said: "The John Lewis Partnership
OL,11,Fhas a plan to return to profit, which
OL,12,Finvolves investing heavily to enhance
OL,13,Four customer offer, technology, stores
OL,14,Fand becoming more efficient.
OL,16,F"This is working and performance is
OL,17,Fimproving, but as we have already
OL,18,Fannounced, that sadly means reducing
OL,19,Fthe number of Partners we need in our
OL,20,Fbusiness.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
