OL,6,F"It would be inappropriate to discuss
OL,7,Fdetails and our Partners will be the
OL,8,Ffirst to know about any changes."
OL,10,FThe Guardian detailed that "rising pay
OL,11,Fand other costs and poor sales" are a
OL,12,Ffew of the reasons behind the
OL,13,Fdecision, as the company battles to
OL,14,Fbounce back from a #230m full-year
OL,15,Floss.
OL,17,FIn a series of messages seen by ITV
OL,18,FNews from the John Lewis intranet,
OL,19,Femployees voiced their frustration at
OL,20,Fthe news.
