OL,6,FAnother said: "After reading this
OL,7,Fannouncement I am angry and dismayed
OL,8,Fthat our 'Leadership Team' think that
OL,9,Fthe way this decision has been reached
OL,10,Fand communicated is acceptable,
OL,11,Fespecially as we are about to go
OL,12,Fthrough a period of change with what a
OL,13,Flot of Partners are now assuming will
OL,14,Finvolve numerous redundancies... When
