OL,3,CJohn Lewis confirms plans to cut
OL,4,Cworkforce over the next five years
OL,6,FThe company has cut thousands of jobs
OL,7,Fsince it launched its turnaround plan
OL,8,Falmost four years ago, through the
OL,9,Fclosure of high street stores as well
OL,10,Fas head office redundancies.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, it was announced that the
OL,13,Fcompany is to halve its redundancy pay
OL,14,Fpackage for workers as the troubled
OL,15,Fretail giant continues to slash costs
OL,16,Fas part of its major overhaul.
