OL,3,CJohn Lewis confirms plans to cut
OL,4,Cworkforce over the next five years
OL,6,FThe move has ratcheted up concerns
OL,7,Fthat more job cuts could be imminent
OL,8,Fat the retail group, which runs the
OL,9,Fdepartment store chain and Waitrose
OL,10,Fgrocery business.
OL,12,FWorkers were informed on Thursday
OL,13,Fmorning that the group will water down
OL,14,Fpart of its partnership redundancy pay
OL,15,Fplan.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
