OL,3,CJohn Lewis confirms plans to cut
OL,4,Cworkforce over the next five years
OL,6,FIt said the group's redundancy pay
OL,7,Fpackage, which gives workers two weeks
OL,8,Fof redundancy pay for every year at
OL,9,Fthe business, will be reduced by half
OL,10,Fto provide one week of pay per year as
OL,11,Fa partner.
OL,13,FThis is in addition to statutory
OL,14,Fredundancy pay.
OL,16,FJLP said the move will provide it with
OL,17,Fmore funds to put towards supporting
OL,18,Fits budgets and could be put towards
OL,19,Fits next pay review.
